## Typography System

### Font Files

- **Houstiq.otf**: Serif font for headings and brand text
  - Format: OpenType
  - Usage: Headings, elegant statements
  - Loaded via `@font-face`

- **BDOGrotesk-VF.ttf**: Variable sans-serif font
  - Format: TrueType Variable Font
  - Weight range: 300-900
  - Usage: Body text, labels, navigation
  - Loaded via `@font-face` with variable weight support

### Font Loading

```css
@font-face {
  font-family: Houstiq;
  src: url('../fonts/Houstiq.otf') format("opentype");
  font-display: swap;
}

@font-face {
  font-family: Bdogrotesk Vf;
  src: url('../fonts/BDOGrotesk-VF.ttf') format("truetype");
  font-weight: 300 900;
  font-display: swap;
}
```

